              ELSE
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC       TO COCV7810-XDESCCPRAZO1
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *--- Ocorrencia 01 - Tipo de Factura
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV7810-CTIPFAC1 NOT EQUAL SPACES
             MOVE CON-CTABELA-CTIPFAC     TO WS-CTABELA
             MOVE COCV7810-CTIPFAC1       TO WS-CCOD
             MOVE SPACES                  TO WS-C2COD
