              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CIMPOSTO    TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE COCV7810-CIMPOSTO2      TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES                  TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S      TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO2-S
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-CAPLIC TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO2-CAPLIC
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-MSG    TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO2-MSG
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC       TO COCV7811-XDESCCIMPOSTO2
              ELSE
