               MOVE TGCL1000-GDESC       TO COCV7811-XDESCCTIPFAC3
             ELSE
               MOVE TGCL1000-GDESC       TO COCV7810-XDESCCTIPFAC3
             END-IF
           END-IF.
      *--- Ocorrencia 03 - Tipo de Imposto
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND COCV7810-CIMPOSTO3 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CIMPOSTO    TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE COCV7810-CIMPOSTO3      TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES                  TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 2200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S      TO COCV7811-CIMPOSTO3-S
